Uses of Package
org.perfidix.element

Packages that use org.perfidix.element
org.perfidix * This is the main package which has Benchmark as the main component of the framework and Perfidix as an external starting point. 
org.perfidix.element * Related classes to handle the methods to be executed are located in this package as well as the invoking framework and the different kinds of arrangement for the execution of the benchmarkable methods. 
org.perfidix.socketadapter This class offers all possibilties to hand on a Perclipse Plugin.
